OL,3,CSchool worker who says she was sacked
OL,4,Cfor being Christian wins right to
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FA school worker who claims she was
OL,8,Fsacked because of her Christian
OL,9,Fbeliefs has won the right for her
OL,10,Fappeal against her dismissal to be
OL,11,Fheard by senior judges.
OL,13,FKristie Higgs, 47, was dismissed for
OL,14,Fgross misconduct by Farmor's School in
OL,15,FFairford, Gloucestershire, in 2019
OL,16,Fafter sharing Facebook posts
OL,17,Fcriticising plans to teach LGBT+
OL,18,Frelationships in primary schools.
