OL,4,Cfor being Christian wins right to
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FIn its ruling in 2020, the tribunal
OL,8,Fconcluded her religion is a "protected
OL,9,Fcharacteristic" as defined by the
OL,10,FEquality Act but the school lawfully
OL,11,Fdismissed her.
OL,13,FMrs Higgs appealed against that
OL,14,Fjudgment to the Employment Appeal
OL,15,FTribunal in London, which ruled in her
OL,16,Ffavour and remitted the case back to
OL,17,Fan employment tribunal for a fresh
OL,18,Fdetermination.
