OL,7,FMrs Higgs's lawyers appealed the
OL,8,Fdecision to order a fresh employment
OL,9,Ftribunal hearing and have now won the
OL,10,Fright to have her case heard by Court
OL,11,Fof Appeal judges.
OL,13,FThe hearing is likely to take place
OL,14,Flater this year.
OL,16,FMrs Higgs welcomed the fresh hearing.
