OL,7,F"From the beginning, despite the many
OL,8,Fattempts by the school to suggest
OL,9,Fotherwise, this has always been about
OL,10,Fmy Christian beliefs and me being
OL,11,Fdiscriminated against for expressing
OL,12,Fthem in my own time," she said.
OL,14,F"I was, and still am, appalled by the
OL,15,Fsexual ideology that was being
OL,16,Fintroduced to my son's Church of
OL,17,FEngland primary school.
