OL,7,F"What has happened since in schools
OL,8,Fwith extreme RSE (relationships and
OL,9,Fsex education) and transgender
OL,10,Fideology shows that I was right to be
OL,11,Fconcerned as a parent."
OL,13,FMrs Higgs, from Fairford,
OL,14,FGloucestershire, shared and commented
OL,15,Fon posts which raised concerns about
OL,16,Frelationship education at her son's
OL,17,FChurch of England primary school.
