OL,4,Cfor being Christian wins right to
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FPupils were to learn about the No
OL,8,FOutsiders In Our School programme,
OL,9,Fwhich is a series of books teaching
OL,10,Fthe Equality Act in primary schools.
OL,12,FMrs Higgs, who was posting on Facebook
OL,13,Funder her maiden name, shared two
OL,14,Fposts in October 2018 to about 100
OL,15,Ffriends.
OL,17,FOne of the posts referred to
OL,18,F"brainwashing our children".
