OL,7,FAn anonymous complaint was made to the
OL,8,Fschool and Mrs Higgs was suspended
OL,9,Fand, after a disciplinary hearing,
OL,10,Fdismissed for gross misconduct.
OL,12,FAndrea Williams, chief executive of
OL,13,Fthe Christian Legal Centre, said: "The
OL,14,Fprevious judgment that upheld her
OL,15,Fsacking could not stand.
OL,17,F"In what should have been a cut and
OL,18,Fdry case of discrimination, however,
OL,19,Fit has been unnerving to encounter the
OL,20,Fseries of obstacles blocking Kristie
OL,21,Fsecuring justice.
