OL,7,F"We now press on in this important
OL,8,Fcase.
OL,10,F"For Kristie's case to be heard at the
OL,11,FCourt of Appeal is a huge moment for
OL,12,FChristian freedoms and the freedom of
OL,13,Fany employee to be able to express
OL,14,Fopposition to LGBT+ ideology without
OL,15,Ffear of losing their jobs."
